entries.title_d: The Empire has important supplies for our forces in the Naboo System. Our efforts there are important and should be disrupted by such petty problems as a lack of supplies.  You are to escort the supply freighters as they enter the system.
entries.title: Naboo System: Escort the Imperial Freighters Duty
entries.thanks_5: I just don't understand why they would want to attack us like that.
entries.thanks_4: Not very good pirates, are they.
entries.thanks_3: How did they know we were here?
entries.thanks_2: Who do you think they were?
entries.thanks_1: You are a credit to the uniform.
entries.taunt_5: Feel the sting of the Alliance.
entries.taunt_4: We don't know why you are here, but it can't be good!
entries.taunt_2: You will fall to my might.
entries.shields_depleted: Our shields are down! You'd best start doing a better job protecting us, pilot.
entries.reason_5: Hello, pilot. Imperial freighter FR4-9q12 in route to drop off supplies reporting in.
entries.reason_4: Hello, pilot. Imperial freighter FR8-0s09 in route to drop off supplies reporting in.
entries.reason_3: Hello, pilot. Imperial freighter FR9-7y41 in route to drop off supplies reporting in.
entries.reason_2: Hello, pilot. Imperial freighter FR6-6f02 in route to drop off supplies reporting in.
entries.reason_1: Hello, pilot. Imperial freighter FR3-9b23 in route to drop off supplies reporting in.
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Travel to the supplied navigaiton waypoint and wait for the Imperial freighter to arrive.
entries.quest_location_d: Meet the Imperial Freighters as they enter the Naboo System.
entries.quest_escort_d: Follow and protect the Imperial freighter to it's drop location. Remain alert for Rebel fighters.
entries.panic_3: How did they know we were here?
entries.hull_half: Hull integrety down to fifity percent. We are not going to last much longer unless you get those fighters off of us.
entries.goodbye_5: Supplies have been dropped to the surface. Jumping out of the sector now. Thanks, pilot.
entries.goodbye_4: Supplies have been dropped to the surface. Jumping out of the sector now. Thanks, pilot.
entries.goodbye_3: Supplies have been dropped to the surface. Jumping out of the sector now. Thanks, pilot.
entries.goodbye_2: Supplies have been dropped to the surface. Jumping out of the sector now. Thanks, pilot.
entries.goodbye_1: Supplies have been dropped to the surface. Jumping out of the sector now. Thanks, pilot.
entries.found_loc: We have sent the arrival location to your nav computer. Wait at that location for the arrival of the freighter and escort it safely through the sector.
entries.failed_protect: You have failed in your duty with your cowardice. Report your failed to your commander.
entries.failed_destroy: Your orders were to keep that ship safe. Report your failure to your superior.
entries.complete: The freighter has safely made it's delivery. Stand by to help escort another ship or return to your superior to check in.
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:\#pcontrast3 <Warning! Enemy ships detected. Incoming at high speeds.>
entries.arrived_at_loc: Hold your current position until the arrival of the freighter we are to escort.
entries.abort: \#FF0000 Pilot, your orders were clear. You were to escort us to the drop location.
